{"tid":622220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西甲前瞻：C朗大勇 皇馬誓贏打吡爭亞軍","createTime":"2018-04-09T03:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T13:13:08.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"210d6b668c891fbdacbdd03cce5a45d8cd0f8762","tid":622220,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"不論是目前排第3名的皇馬及第2名的馬體會，兩軍要爭取成為聯賽冠軍基本已經無望，惟今仗卻直接影響聯賽亞軍誰屬。目前皇馬以4分之差後落馬體會排第3，但只要今仗擊敗這支同市死敵即能收窄差距至1分，故相信他們雖有歐聯8強次回合對祖雲達斯的大戰，但仍會派出強陣應戰。皇馬攻擊陣容方面，料會以大勇的C朗拿度及賓施馬掛帥，中場配合馬高阿辛斯奧及盧卡斯華斯基斯作兩翼支援。傷兵方面他們僅有拿祖費南迪斯肯定不能上陣，其他球員都可供施丹調配。"},{"pid":"4042f93c3d2536bf02a63ccaf5de849ec2cdaade","tid":622220,"uid":43652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465637bfa4f2feed8d86da5863bfa86cb95ee425","tid":622220,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7153d40553918771162b256e256f31184f5dea52","tid":622220,"uid":31475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"倒掛&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62ba99ba73b2d5728e90565ed7a62f234b18ade","tid":622220,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00a39691dc2d4e4d41a7bfc8ff046a97912c254","tid":622220,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"入球<img src=